.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/PCDM/111%2c%e7%b0%a1%2c463%2c20220427%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"PCDM,111,簡,463,20220427,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"簡","JNO":"463","JDATE":"20220427","JTITLE":"傷害"}